CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 31, 1959, pg. A16 reads: "Marie Jeanne will model some of her own exquisite creations at the fashion show Nov. 6 at the A. Leo Weil School, sponsored by members of the young Women's Board of Ushers of Wesley Center AME Zion Church. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "Marie Jeanne" Mary Jane Shipman Brown modeling dark short sleeve dress, dark gloves, and floral wrap in interior doorway, with broadside on floor reading "Les Femmes Modistes presents, Canada Caper Fashion Preview, Marie Jeanne originals, Belinda Blandburg, hat designs, Marlene Moore, commentary, Bobby Jones at the organ, Sunday May 24, 1959 , Theresa L Kaufmann auditorium, 1835 Centre Avenue..."
